- content_for :title, "Try the redesign"
%div{class: "max-w-2xl mx-auto my-10 v2-card text-center"}
  %h1{class: "v2-page-title mb-3"} Try the new serveme.tf
  %p{class: "text-muted mb-5"}
    We're testing a refreshed look. It's opt-in and only changes your view —
    everyone else keeps the current site. You can switch back any time.
  - if beta_ui?
    = button_to "Switch back to the classic look", beta_disable_path, method: :delete, class: "v2-btn v2-btn-ghost"
  - else
    = button_to "Try the new look", beta_enable_path, method: :post, class: "v2-btn v2-btn-primary"
